snippet.title: Again "Ding-dong": Amber Heard reportedly still fighting for bigger Aquaman 2 role
snippet.description: Aquaman 2 is due to start shooting this summer, but right now we still don’t know for certain how involved Amber Heard will be in the DC sequel. Rumors swirled a few weeks ago that the actress was to be replaced as Mera due to poor health, however this was soon refuted by her reps. Nevertheless, reports say Warner Bros. is at least attempting to reduce her presence in the movie, given all the bad press that surrounds her these days.
